b'Burn Up Scramble':
b'AD. 2023, Tokyo. Because of the change of the society such as internationalization and enlargement of the trading, the dark side of the society also continues changing. The criminals are getting deep, and their organizations are increasing its size, then the peace and security is getting worse.

The government takes it seriously, and decides to introduce an innovative system. In order to cope with the special criminals, an extralegal police is founded. 

It is a special criminal team, Warriors, which consists of a few elite members. 

(Source: AnimeNfo)'
